fields.description: The additional HTTP headers in the request to RESTful API used for authorization. Type: key value pairs (value should be string type).
fields.name: AuthHeaders

fields.description: The authentication type to be used to connect to the HTTP server.
fields.name: AuthenticationType

fields.description: Thumbprint of certificate for ClientCertificate authentication. Only valid for on-premises copy. For on-premises copy with ClientCertificate authentication, either CertThumbprint or EmbeddedCertData/Password should be specified. Type: string (or Expression with resultType string).
fields.name: CertThumbprint

fields.description: Base64 encoded certificate data for ClientCertificate authentication. For on-premises copy with ClientCertificate authentication, either CertThumbprint or EmbeddedCertData/Password should be specified. Type: string (or Expression with resultType string).
fields.name: EmbeddedCertData

fields.description: If true, validate the HTTPS server SSL certificate. Default value is true. Type: boolean (or Expression with resultType boolean).
fields.name: EnableServerCertificateValidation

fields.description: The encrypted credential used for authentication. Credentials are encrypted using the integration runtime credential manager. Type: string.
fields.name: EncryptedCredential

fields.description: The base URL of the HTTP endpoint, e.g. https://www.microsoft.com. Type: string (or Expression with resultType string).
fields.name: Url

fields.description: User name for Basic, Digest, or Windows authentication. Type: string (or Expression with resultType string).
fields.name: UserName
